com.salesforce.androidsdk.ui
Interface SalesforceR

public interface SalesforceR

Since the SalesforceSDK is packaged as a jar, it can't have resources. Class that allows references to resources defined outside the SDK. Projects making use of the SDK need to provide an implementation.
